author: IANS
title: North East United FC replace Miguel Garcia with Andre Bikey
text: > Guwahati : Indian Super League (ISL) club NorthEast United FC on Tuesday confirmed that they have signed Cameroon defender Andre Bikey as a replacement for the injured Miguel Garcia. “Miguel Garcia had suffered an Achilles tendon rupture earlier this season, requiring a recovery time of 10 to 12 weeks,” NorthEast United said in a release. The 30-year-old Bikey was a free agent having last played for England Championship side Charlton Athletic.
